    public interface Annotation

    A representation of the model object 'Annotation'. Annotation is an element that allows specifying on an annotated element additional details that do not have associated DL semantics. An annotation specifies the value of an annotation property on an annotated element. It can be specified either directly on an annotated element or indirectly on a reference to one.

    The following features are supported:

    • Property
    • Value
    • Owning Element
    • Owning Reference
